    <item>
      <title>全球债券抛售导致美国国债收益率逼近 5%</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-08/key-us-treasury-yields-approach-2023-peaks-with-5-in-sight</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于对通胀上升、政治动荡和政府债务膨胀的担忧不断加剧，全球债券市场持续爆发的抛售正迅速将收益率推向关键门槛。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-08/key-us-treasury-yields-approach-2023-peaks-with-5-in-sight</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 08 Jan 2025 13:40:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>股市挣扎，交易员为就业市场动荡做准备：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-07/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于交易员不愿进行高风险押注，股市下跌，市场将在周五就业报告公布前夕收盘。美国国债收益率飙升，令全球投资者感到不安，之后国债价格趋于稳定。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-07/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 07 Jan 2025 22:33:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>埃克森美孚股价下跌，因警告称石油和炼油业务将影响第四季度利润</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-07/exxon-predicts-700-million-hit-to-profit-from-lower-oil-prices</link>
      <description><![CDATA[埃克森美孚公司股价下跌，此前该公司警告称，其第四季度收益将受到 2024 年最后三个月原油价格下跌和炼油利润率收窄的打击。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-07/exxon-predicts-700-million-hit-to-profit-from-lower-oil-prices</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 07 Jan 2025 22:21:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
